      "description": "Block a Duo user by UserID.\n\nNote that this action uses the Duo Admin API which is not enabled by default. You may need to contact Duo Support and ask for the admin API to be enabled. You can then create an application with integration and secret keys following the normal process in your Duo admin panel.\n\n[] Generate a list of parameters to POST to Duo\n[] Assemble the request URL\n[] Generate a signed signature for the request\n[] Send the request to Duo\n[] Extract the response values\n[] Set the workflow's output variables\n[] Check if there was an error\n\nAPI information: https://duo.com/docs/adminapi",
